@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Air Transport Company Collaborator" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC

ATCC -> System : Requests to add an aircraft to company fleet

activate System
System --> ATCC : Requests aircraft data, model and cabin configuration
deactivate System

ATCC -> System : Provides aircraft data

activate System
System --> System : Check if collaborator is authorized
System --> System : Validate air transport company
System --> System : Check if collaborator belongs to company
System --> System : Validate aircraft model
System --> System : Validate engine configuration
System --> System : Validate registration number
System --> System : Check registration number uniqueness
System --> System : Validate registered country
System --> System : Validate cabin configuration
System --> System : Check total seats do not exceed model capacity
System --> System : Validate number of flight crew members
System --> System : Validate operational status

alt aircraft data is valid
    System --> System : Add aircraft to company fleet
    System --> ATCC : Aircraft added successfully
else aircraft data is invalid
    System --> ATCC : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate ATCC

@enduml